body:
I have been having this problem for a while, my textures seem to stretch off their models while gaming, it seems to happen in everygame i play,since the fullscreen problem with some players occurs.I was affected and now playin the game on windowed mode.But that isnt the biggest problem,these graphical glitches...

Here it is a screen shot of it: https://s24.postimg.org/6e7l9gu5h/glitch.jpg



It happens every so often, sometimes it never happens for hours sometimes the game is riddiled with multiple models skewing their textures.When i use Vertical sync or change my in game resolution(from video settings in the game),the texture glitches disappear for a while,then the same again.I dont have this problem with other games im playin with much greater system requirements. I have no idea how to fix this problem or really what causes them.If anyone could help me, please do.   {{champion:32}}
